[[File:Axel_Dench.jpg|thumb|200px|Axel Dench.]]'''Axel Dench''' played [[Merumeru/Legends|Merumeru]] in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. Also in his career he has starred in films such as [[Wikipedia:Bill & Ted's Excellent Adventure|''Bill & Ted's Excellent Adventure'']], [[Wikipedia:Flight of the Navigator|''Flight of the Navigator'']], [[Wikipedia:Twins (film)|''Twins'']] and hit TV series [[Wikipedia:Grange Hill|''Grange Hill'']]

Dench, who stands at 6'11" and weighs 243 lbs, has also played professional basketball in Australia's National Basketball League for the Wollongong Hawks and Melbourne Tigers. He currently works in Fund Settlements for La Trobe Financial in Melbourne, Australia.

